sentences.english: The peasants here were of a much poorer class than those in Kousminski.
sentences.chinese: 這裏的農民比庫茲明斯科耶的農民要窮得多。

sentences.english: If you have not broken samaya, you will become Buddha eventually.
sentences.chinese: 你若未破三昧耶，你終將成佛。

sentences.english: It is now "clearly in double-digit territory, " says Mr Niedermayer.
sentences.chinese: 並將其“明確在兩位數的範圍”，內德梅耶說。

sentences.english: It's good to worship God, so you will be blessed.
sentences.chinese: 好耶，拜多了神，神自然會保祐你啦。

sentences.english: And yet we actually say “Yeah, we should”.
sentences.chinese: 不過我們實際上依然在說，“耶，我們應該這樣做。”

sentences.english: Homer and Langley Collyer were found dead in their home in nineteen forty-seven.
sentences.chinese: 荷馬和蘭利科爾耶發現它們在一九四七年死於家。

sentences.english: In May, I made the decision to nominate Judge Breyer.
Angela:I don't think this is good for me. I think I need to go on a diet.
sentences.chinese: 但我覺得這樣好像不太好耶，我想我應該要減肥了。

sentences.english: I just get my parole, and do not want to be your scapegoat somehow.
sentences.chinese: 我纔剛剛假釋耶，不想莫名其妙的變成你的代罪羔羊。

sentences.english: Ensnared in maya, I am all but dead.
sentences.chinese: 在摩耶的誘捕下，我差點兒死去。

sentences.english: Also, Jeroboam son of Nebat rebelled against the king.
sentences.chinese: 所羅門的臣僕，尼八的兒子耶羅波安也舉手攻擊王。

sentences.english: There was war between Rehoboam and Jeroboam throughout Abijah's lifetime.
sentences.chinese: 羅波安在世的日子常與耶羅波安爭戰。

sentences.english: Doris:There is snow on Yangmingshan. Let's go visit the mountain together.
sentences.chinese: 陽明山下雪了耶，我們一起上山去看好不好。

sentences.english: "I think the Yeovil player's teeth went into my leg! " he revealed.
sentences.chinese: 我認爲耶奧維爾的球員的牙齒都陷入我的腿裏了。

sentences.english: In chapter 6 we have the Battle of Jericho.
sentences.chinese: 第六章中有耶利亞哥戰役。

sentences.english: Open my eyes, yeah; it was only just a dream.
sentences.chinese: 睜開雙眸，耶，不過碎夢一場。
